    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[This game is currently under development. Wishlist now to be the first notified of its release!]</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137510/extras/0fed6453463f98772d59f50039cfc6b6.avif?t=1763617381\" width=616 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Enjoy some cozy scrapbooking alongside a heartfelt story where you can...</strong></i>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve Puzzles</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From simple and fun puzzles to complex ones, connect the dots using context clues from different aspects of the level and create something new! &lt;3 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137510/extras/0c85e67454cec669b30735752d38791a.poster.avif?t=1763617381\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137510/extras/0c85e67454cec669b30735752d38791a.webm?t=1763617381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137510/extras/0c85e67454cec669b30735752d38791a.mp4?t=1763617381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find Romance</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make choices that will lead Belle to find the love of her life. From celebrity crushes to first loves to forever, introduce a little romance into the mix! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get Scrapbooking </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As it says on the tin. Have fun letting your creativity fly by making different scrapbook spreads per themed level as you listen to some cool tunes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137510/extras/8df671449a4df0c582b39b2342466ad7.poster.avif?t=1763617381\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137510/extras/8df671449a4df0c582b39b2342466ad7.webm?t=1763617381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137510/extras/8df671449a4df0c582b39b2342466ad7.mp4?t=1763617381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make Decisions</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Influence the trajectory of Belle's life with different choices. Will she have her pre-teen goth phase or does she prefer a pop of bubblegum pink instead? Is she a theater kid or a high school cheerleader? What major does she choose in college? It's all up to you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137510/extras/aac03a8da3ad3f8fae03febb76b7d99a.avif?t=1763617381\" width=616 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Help Belle scrapbook the different stages of her life! Including... </i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Childhood </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tween Phases </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High School Life </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >College </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137510/extras/686829d8713220ad540d2e1229ee8d4a.avif?t=1763617381\" width=616 height=139 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Support our small studio!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check out the links on our store page! Whether you help us by donating or by joining our community, every little gesture is a big step toward helping us complete our goals. </p>",
